OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPentagon chief apologises  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor secretive hospital stay
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, US Defence Secretary Lloyd Austin has  
OL,6, apologised after failing to notify the 
OL,7, chain of command when he was secretly  
OL,8, admitted to a hospital in December.    
OL,10,FMr Austin, 70, was released last month 
OL,11,Fas he continues to recover from        
OL,12,Ftreatment for prostate cancer.         
OL,14,F"I did not handle this right," he said.
OL,15,F"I should have told the president about
OL,16,Fmy cancer diagnosis."                  
OL,18,FPentagon chiefs are supposed to be     
OL,19,Favailable at a moment's notice to      
OL,20,Fhandle any national security crisis.   
